---
title: Ras El Hanout Mango Chicken with Carrot Couscous & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Fruity sauces are amazing when they are coated over succulent chicken. The best of them all is this mango chutney!
Let it drizzle into the couscous, tossed with carrot and spinach, for a bowl that is spiced, sweet and definitely
delicious.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

